&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center;&#34;&gt;
Trimethoprim/sulfamethoxazole combination (TMP/SMX) is considered the treatment of choice but can itself lead to AKI, posing a significant challenge in the management of patients with concomitant COVID-19 and S. maltophilia pneumonia. […] The patient subsequently developed superimposed bacterial pneumonia with S. maltophilia requiring administration of TMP/SMX. […] However, TMP/SMX led to the development of AKI, which continued to worsen despite appropriate management including hemodialysis.
